"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">k-Means divides the colors "
"into clusters and refines the assignment at every iteration.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">This is the best option "
"when tracing images with a lot of colors or shading.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">For pictures with a lot of "
"colors increasing the number of iterations will yield better results but it "
"might be slower.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">The <span style=\" font-"
"style:italic;\">Match</span> option performs some post-processing:</p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:12px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">None</span>: Don't "
"perform any post-processing and return the means (note this might result in "
"colors not present in the original image)</li>\n"
"<li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Closest</span>: Find the color in the original image that is "
"the closest to the mean</li>\n"
"<li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Most Frequent</span>: Find the color in the cluster that "
"appears most often in the source image</li></ul></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/"
"REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n"
"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css"
"\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">k-Means rozdelí farby do "
"zhlukov a v každej iterácii spresní priradenie.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Toto je najlepšia voľba "
"pri trasovaní obrázkov s veľkým množstvom farieb alebo tieňovaním.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Pri obrázkoch s veľkým "
"množstvom farieb zvýšenie počtu iterácií prinesie lepšie výsledky, ale môže "
"to byť pomalšie.</p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; "
"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"
"\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Voľba <span style=\" font-"
"style:italic;\">Zhoda</span> vykoná dodatočné spracovanie:</p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-"
"right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:12px; "
"margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; "
"text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:600;\">Žiadna</span>: "
"Nevykonať žiadne dodatočné spracovanie a vrátiť priemery (upozorňujeme, že "
"to môže viesť k farbám, ktoré nie sú prítomné v pôvodnom obrázku)</li>\n"
"<li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Najbližšia</span>: Nájsť v pôvodnom obrázku farbu, ktorá je "
"najbližšie k priemeru</li>\n"
"<li style=\"\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; "
"margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Najčastejšia</span>: Nájsť v zhluku farbu, ktorá sa v "
"zdrojovom obrázku vyskytuje najčastejšie</li></ul></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (plainText), widget (QPlainTextEdit, plainTextEdit)
#: src/gui/widgets/dialogs/color_quantization_dialog.ui:159
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"k-Modes gives you the colors that appear most often in the source image.\n"
"\n"
"It's very fast but it does not give accurate colors for complex images.\n"
"\n"
"This is the best option when tracing images with flat colors."
msgstr ""
"k-Modes vám poskytne farby, ktoré sa v zdrojovom obrázku vyskytujú "
"najčastejšie.\n"
"\n"
"Je to veľmi rýchle, ale neposkytuje presné farby pre zložité obrázky.\n"
"\n"
"Toto je najlepšia voľba pri trasovaní obrázkov s plochými farbami."

#. i18n: ectx: property (html), widget (QTextEdit, textEdit_2)
#: src/gui/widgets/dialogs/color_quantization_dialog.ui:178
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/"
"REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n"
"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css"
"\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">The Octree algorithm "
"merges similar colors from the bottom up.</p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">It gives more accurate "
"colors for complex images but it might result into colors that are not "
"present in the source image.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/"
"REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n"
"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css"
"\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Algoritmus Octree zlučuje "
"podobné farby zdola nahor.</p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Poskytuje presnejšie farby "
"pre zložité obrázky, ale môže viesť k farbám, ktoré nie sú prítomné v "
"zdrojovom obrázku.</p></body></html>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label_4)
#: src/gui/widgets/dialogs/color_quantization_dialog.ui:189
#, kde-format
msgid "Min Frequency"
msgstr "Min. frekvencia"

#. i18n: ectx: property (html), widget (QTextEdit, textEdit_3)
#: src/gui/widgets/dialogs/color_quantization_dialog.ui:205
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/"
"REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n"
"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css"
"\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Edge Exclusion Modes takes "
"the most frequent color (mode) in the image, then excludes all pixels "
"touching said area, then repeats the process until the appropriate number of "
"colors has been found.</p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">This approach removes anti-"
"aliased edges but it might cause small details to not be detected.</p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Min Frequency</span> refers to the minimum amount of pixels "
"that a color must have to be considered (as a percentage of the total number "
"of pixels in the image).</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/"
"REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n"
"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css"
"\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Noto Sans'; font-size:10pt; font-"
"weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Režim vylúčenia okrajov "
"vezme najčastejšiu farbu (modus) v obrázku, potom vylúči všetky pixely "
"dotýkajúce sa danej oblasti a potom opakuje tento proces, kým sa nenájde "
"príslušný počet farieb.</p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Tento prístup odstraňuje "
"vyhladzované okraje, ale môže spôsobiť, že malé detaily nebudú rozpoznané.</"
"p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-"
"right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-"
"weight:600;\">Min. frekvencia</span> označuje minimálny počet pixelov, ktorý "
"musí farba mať, aby bola zohľadnená (ako percento z celkového počtu pixelov "
"v obrázku).</p></body></html>"

